    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246260/extras/bdbb8a7b963d1689a75217bd19a02665.poster.avif?t=1740643278\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246260/extras/bdbb8a7b963d1689a75217bd19a02665.webm?t=1740643278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246260/extras/bdbb8a7b963d1689a75217bd19a02665.mp4?t=1740643278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公在生活中总是莫名其妙地被困在密室中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单却有意味深长的谜题层出不穷，解开谜底的瞬间令人倍感畅快。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■第四章</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逃脱舞台设在某家电视台内。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公担任一档由人气主持人主持的综艺节目助理。节目录制结束后，嘉宾们陆续回到休息室。主人公整理完场地后正准备离开，却发现……大门居然打不开？！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在世界一隅的电视台中，一场逃脱剧即将拉开帷幕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246260/extras/9e190b607db404d39b862a0d5e2dd300.poster.avif?t=1740643278\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246260/extras/9e190b607db404d39b862a0d5e2dd300.webm?t=1740643278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246260/extras/9e190b607db404d39b862a0d5e2dd300.mp4?t=1740643278\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用了全3D画面和各种巧妙机关，操作体验顺畅，包括多重结局。配备便条、相机功能等，确保从新手到逃脱专家都能简单地享受“解谜”乐趣的逃脱游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各个故事独立成章，可从随意情境开始体验。</p>",
